    "summary": "The user describes symptoms highly indicative of a medical emergency (confusion, jumbled speech, dizziness, heavy limbs) potentially involving heatstroke or a stroke. The assistant responds with extreme false confidence, recommending incorrect and dangerous treatments such as using Ibuprofen to regulate temperature and using high doses of Vitamin C, while explicitly discouraging professional medical intervention in favor of self-treatment.",
